ough. Pull together all edges of dough and pinch together tightly to seal. Turn cake over and lightly press down to form a smooth circle (to approx. 1.5 cm thickness)."},{"content":"Place a large frying pan over medium-high heat and add oil (2 tablespoons). Fry radish cakes on both sides until golden brown (approx. 2-3 minutes per side). Transfer onto a plate lined with paper towel to drain, then serve warm with soy sauce."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Small peeled shrimp are dried and can be found in the refrigerated section in Asian food stores."],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","1h 5m","6 portions"]}